<i>menyentuh mereka...</i>

24
00:02:39,944 --> 00:02:41,064
<i>...karena mereka keluargamu.</i>

25
00:02:42,221 --> 00:02:44,556
<i>Baiklah, kalau begitu.</i>
<i>Aku mendukungmu...</i>

26
00:02:44,603 --> 00:02:49,176
<i>...dengan Symphonia Domestica</i>
<i>oleh Richard Strauss.</i>

27
00:03:25,256 --> 00:03:26,816
