<i>Dia CEO perusahaan</i>
<i>tempat Se-hyuk bekerja.</i>

83
00:07:07,496 --> 00:07:10,656
<i>Bagaimana perasaan Se-hyuk</i>
<i>jika CEO menikahi adikmu?</i>

84
00:07:11,456 --> 00:07:13,496
